OL,3,CM6 driver filmed inhaling balloon hit
OL,4,Cwith six points and #700 fine
OL,6,FA man who was caught on camera
OL,7,Finhaling from a balloon while driving
OL,8,Falong the M6 has been hit with six
OL,9,Fpoints on his licence and a #726 fine.
OL,11,FThe footage released by West Midlands
OL,12,FPolice is one in a series of driving
OL,13,Fconvictions resulting from videos sent
OL,14,Finto the force by members of the
OL,15,Fpublic.
OL,17,FIt says it's received over 11,000
OL,18,Fvideos to its dashcam portal in the
OL,19,Flast year.
