OL,3,CM6 driver filmed inhaling balloon hit
OL,4,Cwith six points and #700 fine
OL,6,FThe video, filmed by the passenger in
OL,7,Fanother car, shows a man driving a
OL,8,Fgrey BMW southbound down the M6 while
OL,9,Finhaling the contents of a yellow
OL,10,Fballoon.
OL,12,FWest Midlands Police are encouraging
OL,13,Fdrivers to send through footage
OL,14,Fshowing driving offences in a bid to
OL,15,Fmake roads safer.
