OL,3,CM6 driver filmed inhaling balloon hit
OL,4,Cwith six points and #700 fine
OL,6,FAmong the clips posted by police is
OL,7,Fdashcam footage of the moment a driver
OL,8,Fwent through a red light and narrowly
OL,9,Fmissing someone crossing the road.
OL,10,FThey were banned from driving for a
OL,11,Fyear, had to take an extended driving
OL,12,Fretest and ordered to pay a #2,649
OL,13,Ffine.
OL,15,FAnother driver received six points and
OL,16,F#1,034 in costs and fines for a close
OL,17,Fpass on a cyclist on Kings Heath High
OL,18,FStreet, while a taxi driver was given
OL,19,Fsix points and a #400 fine for using
OL,20,Ftheir phone.
