OL,3,CM6 driver filmed inhaling balloon hit
OL,4,Cwith six points and #700 fine
OL,6,FFootage sent in by a driver who was
OL,7,Fbeing tailgated by a silver Peugeot in
OL,8,Fa road rage incident on Lichfield Road
OL,9,Fin Wolverhampton led to a #150 fine
OL,10,Fand five points.
OL,12,FOperation Snap received just 208
OL,13,Freports in 2017, in contrast to this
OL,14,Fyear's 11,000.
OL,16,FSgt Steve Evans, who heads up the
OL,17,Fteam, said: "Road safety is an
OL,18,Fabsolute priority for West Midlands
OL,19,FPolice and the work of our team is
OL,20,Fmaking a real difference.
