OL,6,F"Around 90 per cent of the submissions
OL,7,Fwe get end in positive action. That
OL,8,Fcan be everything from a warning
OL,9,Fletter, up to prosecution and a day in
OL,10,Fcourt. One driver has previously
OL,11,Freceived a suspended prison sentence
OL,12,Fas a result of footage sent to the Op
OL,13,FSnap team.
